description:
Photoshop CC is the most powerful photo and image editing tool available. Find out how to get up and running quickly with Photoshop CC. This hands on course walks you through a complete project while showing some of the great features available in Photoshop CC.

You'll learn all of the following:

  • Stepping Into Photoshop CC
  • Selection Tool
  • Seeing Double - The Clone Tool
  • Adjustment Layers For Quick, Impressive Results
  • Typography In Detail
  • Saving Your Work and Creating New Images

This course is a great hands-on, introduction to Photoshop CC that gets you and up running quickly. You'll get a lot out of it and enjoy what your learning along the way!
title: Photoshop CC Tutorial Quick Start
